HEADWORD: Ignoscible
<hw>Ig*nos"ci*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>ignoscibilis</ets>, fr. <ets>ignoscere</ets> to pardon, lit., not
to wish to know; pref. <ets>in-</ets> not + <ets>gnoscere</ets>,
<ets>noscere</ets>, to learn to know. See <er>In-</er> not, and
<er>Know</er>.]</ety> <def>Pardonable.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Bailey.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
